Introduction

Triple iz (Korean: 트리플 이즈) is a South Korean project girl group under The Waves Inc.. The unit consists of Secret Number's Dita, ICHILLIN's E.JI, and X:IN's Aria. They made their debut on April 8, 2024 with the single "Halla".
